aking photos throughout my entire life. My interest in picture making, led me to my first career in advertising and business where I was constantly surrounded by graphic and engaging imagery. After years of soul searching, I finally took the plunge and was accepted to the Art Institute of Chicago, where my photography and art career started! My various backgrounds constantly inspire and create my photography perspectives and my shooting style.\r\n<h2>Style:</h2>\r\nPhotojournalism, cinema, and art are the elements that I strive for in narrating weddings, events and stories. I also love subtle vintage palettes and color combinations which are an important part of my post-production process. During each and every shoot, I love to have fun and create images that showcase personality, style, and quintessential moments. With my photography influences and background, my goal is provide all of my clients with modern and timeless images, with some artistic, spontaneous fun!','about me','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2011-03-02 10:20:47','2011-03-02 17:20:47','',0,'http://dawnephoto.com/dev/',0,'page','',0),(266,1,'2010-08-28 12:08:22','2010-08-28 19:08:22','','About','','inherit','closed','open','','265-revision','','','2010-08-28 12:08:22','2010-08-28 19:08:22','',265,'http://dawnephoto.com/dev/blog/2010/08/28/265-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(267,1,'2010-08-28 12:09:31','2010-08-28 19:09:31','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras eget vulputate enim. Pellentesque ullamcorper sem vel felis rhoncus feugiat. Phasellus dictum luctus varius. Morbi quis ipsum et nulla hendrerit pellentesque. Duis fringilla odio in mauris varius hendrerit. Aenean ut augue quam. Duis lobortis, quam gravida elementum lacinia, ligula sem sagittis nisl, at ultricies elit felis eu lorem. Praesent imperdiet, lectus a semper viverra, sapien erat ullamcorper lacus, eu sollicitudin nulla enim quis metus. Suspendisse nec tellus sem. Cras diam mi, sollicitudin in 