you a Special folder of my favorite images (estimated 20-30) that have been retouched with special effects and filters. At no charge, I can apply filters up to 15 images of your choice.  Online proofing is also available for you on Pictage.com, along with print ordering for your friends and family. An Engagement session or After The Day session is also included in this package along with a $200 album credit if you do decide to order an album.\r\n\r\nPlease inquire about pricing on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/dev/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page if you need coverage for less or more time than the standard 8 hour package. I would be happy to customize a package  based on what you need for your special day. Also, please send me information about your wedding on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/dev/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page, I would love to hear from you!\r\n<h2>Albums</h2>\r\nAlbum pricing varies with size, cover option, pages and images with an average range of $700-$1000 for a full wedding album. Smaller parent books and companion books are also available for $300-$500.  All books are custom-made and designed using your favorite images and design layout preferences. Album manufacturers include Finao, Leather Craftsmen, and Vision Art Books.\r\n<h2>Engagement Sessions</h2>\r\nEngagement sessions along with Day After sessions are available for more casual portraiture as an addition to your wedding prints.  Engagement sessions start at $400 for 2 hours of shooting time, unlimited locations and wardrobe changes.  If wedding packages are purchased, an Engagement Session of After The Day session is automatically included with most packages.  Engagement Sessions are always recommended, but if you decide to forego an engagement session, a credit will be added to your wedding package including an additional hour of wedding coverage or album credit.\r\n\r\n<em>Prices are subject to change without notice. One-third of your total price is 